queries.raw_query:
-- Returns first 100 rows from DATAHUB_COMMUNITY.POSTGRES_PUBLIC.COMPANY
  SELECT 
		AGE,
		ID,
		NAME,
		_FIVETRAN_DELETED,
		_FIVETRAN_SYNCED
 FROM DATAHUB_COMMUNITY.POSTGRES_PUBLIC.COMPANY LIMIT 100;

-- Returns first 100 rows from ETHAN_TEST_DB.PUBLIC.ACCOUNT_PHONE_NUMBER
  SELECT 
		COMMUNICATION_ACCOUNT_ID,
		ID,
		MMS_CAPABLE,
		PHONE_NUMBER,
		SMS_CAPABLE,
		STATUS,
		STATUS_TLM,
		TLM,
		VOICE_CAPABLE,
		WHEN_CREATED
 FROM ETHAN_TEST_DB.PUBLIC.ACCOUNT_PHONE_NUMBER LIMIT 100;
